  <p>Originally from <a href="http://www.thecssninja.com/css/css-tree-menu">CSS Ninja</a>, I've adapted it to use text for the treee markers, use svg images and show an open folder.</p> 

	<ol class="tree">
		<li>
			<input type="checkbox" checked="checked" id="folder1" /> <label for="folder1">Folder 1</label>
